    <div class="card bg-base-100 grid-f">
      <div class="card-body">
        <h2 class="card-title">Insightful polls</h2>
        <p>
          Polls are a useful tool. They are usually part of a conversation and a
          decision process. However, polls are usually not placed where the
          surrounding conversation takes place. Poll results are usually
          imported into a conversation and not kept up to date if more people
          take the poll. In short: polls should claim their rightful place in
          any discussion.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="card bg-base-100 grid-g">
      <div class="card-body">
