    </div>

    <div class="card bg-base-100 grid-h">
      <div class="card-body">
        <h2 class="card-title">Creative brainstorming</h2>
        <p>
          Naive brainstorming immediately devolves into group-think. There is a
          system to creative brainstorming: individual brainstorming first, then
          share, and finally discuss, expand, and refine. All steps can be done
          asynchronously but the first one must and often isn't. In short:
          upgrade every brainstorming session to a creative brainstorming
          session.
        </p>
      </div>
